{"id":53955,"title":"Glycaemic threshold for diabetes-specific retinopathy among individuals from Saudi Arabia, Algeria and Portugal.","abstract":"We studied the glycaemic threshold and prevalence of diabetic retinopathy in screen-detected diabetes in Saudi Arabia, Algeria and Portugal. The prevalence of diabetes-specific retinopathy started to increase at an HbA1c level of 6-6.4% (42-47 mmol/mol) and in individuals with HbA(1c) >7.0% the prevalence was 6.0%.","date":"2014-04-15","categories":"Endocrine System Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24485346","annotations":[{"name":"Diabetes mellitus","weight":0.223912,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diabetes_mellitus"},{"name":"Election threshold","weight":0.0394788,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Election_threshold"},{"name":"Algeria","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Algeria"},{"name":"Diabetic retinopathy","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diabetic_retinopathy"},{"name":"Glycated hemoglobin","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Glycated_hemoglobin"},{"name":"Portugal","weight":0.0287296,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Portugal"},{"name":"Saudi Arabia","weight":0.0287296,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Saudi_Arabia"},{"name":"Prevalence","weight":0.0283361,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Prevalence"},{"name":"Arabian Peninsula","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arabian_Peninsula"},{"name":"Retinopathy","weight":0.0140524,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Retinopathy"}]}
